comment: Harris (DEN) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Redick's (LAC) drive. Redick slips on his own and Harris cleanly strips the ball from him.
Jokic (DEN) makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) who is trying to establish defensive position in the post.
Barton (DEN) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with Jordan's (LAC) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Barton (DEN) moves his pivot foot. The official is looking for any potential illegal contact and does not pick up the pivot foot.
Green (LAC) maintains legal guarding position as he blocks Jokic (DEN) shot attempt.
Gallinari (DEN) does not establish a legal guarding position prior to the contact with Green (LAC).
Paul (LAC) commits a take foul on Mudiay (DEN).
Harris (DEN) makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his RSBQ.
